<plot>A celebration of Hasidic haberdashery, this film describes the qualities of "Mendel's black hats" and the men who wear them. Using mainly documentary footage of a Hasidic rabbi on the streets of Los Angeles, the film delves into what it means to be Hasidic, as symbolized by the signature black hat.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?365739</url></doc>
